commit.message:
Changed the way pathways are plugged in to entourage (fixed #1682)
Other bugfixes/cleanup
worked on plugin mechanism for pathways in entourage

Merged free path node selection with path extension with shift + click
(addressing #1671)
Allowing to select complex node as start and end of a path (fixed #686)

Opening lineup with enroute and added toolbar button to open lineup
(related to #1678)

Fixed #1106 - table perspectives are now removed from pathways, and with
them so are exclamation marks.
